{
  "newspaper_id": "ada-lk",
  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/breaking_news/\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0dca\u200d\u0dba-\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba-\u0d86\u0dba\u0dad\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7-\u0dad\u0dc0\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca-\u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf-\u0db6\u0daf\u0dd4-\u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dca-\u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1-\u0db6\u0dd1/11-396549",
  "time_ut": 1661241421,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0db8\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0d86\u0dba\u0dad\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf \u0db6\u0daf\u0dd4 \u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dd1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "People's tax money can no longer be given to state media organizations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister Bandula Gunawardena said that people's tax money can no longer be given to state media institutions and the money needed to run those institutions should be generated by the institutions.",
        "\"State media institutions are running in a very difficult situation. If we take the real situation, the public's tax money has been given by the public treasury to pay the salaries of the employees of those institutions.",
        "In today's financial difficulties, it is not possible to give money like that. Therefore, I have advised all government media organizations to somehow prepare their own income generation system.",
        "I have instructed the boards of directors to implement a self-retirement system for the excess employees of the company with the money obtained after disposing of those assets that can be disposed of and maintain the company without falling.\""
      ],
